I tested version 7.0.4~8.0.0 to get the following conclusions.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
The Tomee runs the service with the LocalSystem account before version 7.0.6.&lt;br&gt;
Starting with version 7.0.6, the service is run with the LocalService account, so that the permissions are insufficient.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
**The following two ways can solve the issue:**&lt;br&gt;
 - Give the LocalService account access to the directory `AppData\Local\Temp\`.&lt;br&gt;
 - Specifying the Tomee runs the service with the LocalSystem account when installing the service.&lt;br&gt;
